briefdescription.para: File C++ (associated to Stock_Write_Root_Metadata_Part.h) for stock and write metadatas for the ICD6's Root Group.

detaileddescription.para: Overview: Functions stockRootMetadata and writeRootMetadata are described (programmed) here. The first one (stockRootMetadata) will take as parameter all Root Group's metadata and stock them in the private attributes of the class object. The second function (writeRootMetadata) will write them in the hdf5 output file.
